snippet.title: Pumpkin Woods Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2729830/Pumpkin_Woods
Pumpkin Woods Announcement Trailer

Pumpkin Woods is a witch-themed open world survival craft. Collect magical ingredients and build your cozy home while exploring the wonderful sights and secrets of these mysterious lands. Beware though, danger might be lurking deep in these woods...

Developed by Enchanted Pumpkin Co.
Discord: https://discord.gg/warRP5bDFJ
